Create a modern, minimal app icon for a streaming app called StreamSwitch.

Design:
- Circular shape with two arrows forming a loop (symbolizing switching)
- A clean play button in the center
- Minimal, flat design
- No text

Style:
- Dark background
- Green accent color (for savings)
- Slight gradient or glow for modern feel

The logo must be simple, scalable, and recognizable as an app icon.